ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Sex of subject at birth
Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: Unique participant ID associated with Expiwell ambulatory surveys
Breathalyzer reading from BackTrack
Date and time of BAC reading
How much are you currently perspiring? (i.e., how much sweat is on your skin right now?)
How much food have you eaten since the last time you completed a survey?
Notes: 1= Full meal; 2= Half meal; 3= Snack; 4= A few bites

ElementDescription: About how many ounces of non-alcoholic beverage have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (For example, 20 oz is the size of the typical small soda bottle, and 10oz is the size of the average ceramic coffee mug)
What type(s) of non-alcoholic beverages have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (check all that apply) Water
What type(s) of non-alcoholic beverages have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (check all that apply) Caffeinated beverage (coffee, tea, caffeinated sodas, energy drinks)
What type(s) of non-alcoholic beverages have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (check all that apply) Non-caffeinated soft drinks (non-diet)
What type(s) of non-alcoholic beverages have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (check all that apply) Non-caffeinated soft drinks (diet)

What type(s) of non-alcoholic beverages have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (check all that apply) Protein rich beverages (milk, protein drinks, meal replacement, smoothies/shakes)
What type(s) of non-alcoholic beverages have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (check all that apply) Fruit juice/juice-based smoothies
What type(s) of non-alcoholic beverages have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (check all that apply) Other
What type(s) of non-alcoholic beverages have you consumed since the last time you completed a survey? (check all that apply) Other, specify
Type of any drugs or medications taken since the last time you filled out a survey: Stimulants (e.g., Adderall, Ritalin, Cocaine, Methamphetamine)
Type of any drugs or medications taken since the last time you filled out a survey: Opioids (e.g., Heroin, Morphine, Opium, Vicodin, Oxycontin)
